    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Structures or other places of adode that are more than merely temporary, and serve as the usual dwellings of people while at a certain place. In a legal sense, a person may have multiple residences, but only one "domicile," which is their primary dwelling for legal purposes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
